-- Brazil Will Announce BNDES Investment Measure Today
-- B y   C a r l a   S i m o e s
-- 2012-12-05T13:54:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-05/brazil-will-announce-bndes-investment-measure-today-correct-.html
(Corrects headline to say investment measure.)  Brazil ’s government will announce an
expansion of national development bank BNDES’s program to
finance capital goods investments, President Dilma Rousseff
said.  Finance Minister Guido Mantega will announce the expansion
of the so-called PSI program this afternoon, Rousseff said in
Brasilia at the national industry convention.  To contact the reporter on this story:
